text: Furdjel Robby Narsingh (born 13 March 1988) is a Dutch professional footballer who plays as a winger for FC Ararat-Armenia in the Armenian Premier League.Clubloze Furdjel Narsingh tekent nieuw contract bij Cambuur, lc.nl, 5 October 2017 He formerly played for AZ, Volendam, Telstar and PEC Zwolle. ==Career== Born in Amsterdam, Narsingh began his career with Zeeburgia and later joined Jong Ajax. In summer 2006 he signed with AZ Alkmaar and was loaned out in July 2008 to FC Volendam till 30 June 2009. On 19 June 2009, the 21-year-old striker joined Telstar for the 2009–10 season on loan from AZ Alkmaar.Ook Narsingh naar Telstar On 6 July 2011 Furdjel Narsingh joined FC Zwolle.Alexander Bannink en Furdjel Narsingh naar FC Zwolle He promoted to the Eredivisie in 2013. On 28 May 2014, Narsingh signed a one-year deal with SC Cambuur, with an option for another season.Vleugelaanvaller Furdjel Narsingh volgende versterking SC Cambuur In July 2017, he joined League One side Oxford United on trial. However, he was originally confused for his brother Luciano on the team sheet and the club's social media. In October 2017, after one year without a team he rejoined SC Cambuur. ==Personal life== Narsingh is of Indian-SurinameseWorld Cup and Indonesiahttp://old.indianfootball.com/pio- database/index.html descent and has a brother called Luciano who plays for Feyenoord. ==Honours== ===Club=== PEC Zwolle *KNVB Cup (1): 2013–14 *Eerste Divisie (1): 2011–12 Ararat-Armenia * Armenian Premier League (1): 2019–20 * Armenian Supercup (1): 2019 ==References== ==External links== * * Voetbal International profile * Category:Living people Category:1988 births Category:Association football midfielders Category:Dutch footballers Category:Dutch expatriate footballers Category:AFC Ajax players Category:FC Volendam players Category:A.V.V.
